Articles.Content:
Now that Eucl3D has gone under, are there other companies out there who have the files to 3d print KSP designs?

I was going to celebrate my first paycheck with a nice rocket for my office, but it seems I'm a month too late.
I believe it is possible to use a .craft to Blender addon for Blender and modify that for 3D printing then print that, but coloring it will be hard.
